## Cloud Calculator Input Mapping

### AWS Pricing Calculator
**URL**: https://calculator.aws/

| Workload | Instance Type | Qty | vCPUs | RAM | Pricing Model |
|:---|:---|---:|---:|:---|:---|
| Transcoding | `c7i.4xlarge` | 2,540 | 16 | 32 GB | 3yr Reserved (All Upfront) |
| Media/WebRTC | `c7i.2xlarge` | 800 | 8 | 16 GB | 3yr Reserved (All Upfront) |
| App/API | `m7i.2xlarge` | 400 | 8 | 32 GB | 3yr Reserved (All Upfront) |
| Database | `r7i.4xlarge` | 150 | 16 | 128 GB | 3yr Reserved (All Upfront) |
| AI Inference | `c7i.4xlarge` | 125 | 16 | 32 GB | 3yr Reserved (All Upfront) |

**Storage to add:**
- 500 TB gp3 EBS ($0.08/GB/mo)
- 5 PB S3 Standard ($0.023/GB/mo for first 50TB, then tiered)

**Data Transfer:**
- 1,500 TB/month outbound ($0.09/GB after first 100GB)

**Region**: `ap-southeast-1` (Singapore) or `cn-north-1` (Beijing)

